		</div>

	</div>

	<details class="highlight-color-exception-section" data-allow-new-exceptions='yes'>

		<summary>Trello background exceptions</summary>

		<p class="highlight-color-blurb">
			Sometimes itâ€™s good to have a different highlight colour for the different board background types Trello provides. For example, a red list on a red background might not stand out. You can add different highlight colours for different backgrounds here.
		</p>

		<p class="error" data-name="exceptions" data-value="invalid">Please make sure that all options below are valid.</p>

		<ul class="highlight-color-exceptions"></ul>

		<p class="highlight-exceptions-marked-for-deletion invisible">Exceptions marked for deletion will be deleted on save</p>

		<button type="button" id="AddNewException">Add new exception</button>

	</details>

</template>
